com.hazelcast.util

Class UuidUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.util.UuidUtil

  • public final class UuidUtil
extends Object
    Util class to generate type 4 (pseudo randomly generated) UUID.

    Creates UUID of different quality of randomness, which are based on cryptographically weak Random and strong SecureRandom pseudo random number generators.
